    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Having, or abounding in, leaves. May also be used to describe forms resembling leaves, as with lichens and algae having bodies differentiated into stem and leaves.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
